name: API and PNR Passenger Summary By Year

elements.expression:
filters
| demodata
| markdown "

" "" 
  font={font size=14 family="'Open Sans', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif" color="#000000" align="left"}
| render 
  containerStyle={containerStyle backgroundColor="#FFFFFF" border="1px solid #1974D2"}

essql 
  query="SELECT 
airport,count(airport) 
FROM \"message-flight-idx\"
Group By airport"
| dropdownControl valueColumn="airport" filterColumn="airport.keyword"
| render

filters
| demodata
| markdown "Message Type" 
  font={font family="'Open Sans', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif" size=14 align="left" color="#000000" weight="bold" underline=false italic=false}
| render

essql 
  query="SELECT message_type,count(message_type)
FROM \"message-flight-idx\"
Group BY message_type"
| dropdownControl valueColumn="message_type" filterColumn="message_type.keyword"
| render

filters
| demodata
| markdown "Year" 
  font={font family="'Open Sans', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif" size=14 align="left" color="#000000" weight="bold" underline=false italic=false}
| render

essql 
  query="SELECT 
flight_year, count(flight_year)
FROM \"message-flight-idx\"
Group By flight_year"
| dropdownControl valueColumn="flight_year" filterColumn="flight_year.keyword"
| render

filters
| demodata
| markdown ""
| render 
  containerStyle={containerStyle backgroundColor="#BBBBBB" border="1px solid #bfbfbf"}

filters
| demodata
| markdown ""
| render containerStyle={containerStyle border="1px solid #1974D2"}

filters
| essql 
  query="SELECT 
SUM (inbound_passenger_count) as inbound_total
FROM \"message-flight-idx\" "
| math "inbound_total"
| metric "Passengers - Inbound" 
  metricFont={font family="'Open Sans', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif" size=18 align="center" color="#1974D2" weight="bold" underline=false italic=false} 
  labelFont={font size=14 family="'Open Sans', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif" color="#000000" align="center"}
| render

filters
| essql 
  query="SELECT 
SUM (outbound_passenger_count) as outbound_total
FROM \"message-flight-idx\""
| math "outbound_total"
| metric "Passengers - Outbound" 
  metricFont={font family="'Open Sans', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif" size=18 align="center" color="#1974D2" weight="bold" underline=false italic=false} 
  labelFont={font size=14 family="'Open Sans', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif" color="#000000" align="center"}
| render

filters
| essql 
  query="SELECT 
SUM (passenger_count) as pnr_total_passengers
FROM \"message-flight-idx\"
WHERE message_type = 'PNR'"
| math "pnr_total_passengers"
| metric "Passengers - PNR" 
  metricFont={font family="'Open Sans', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif" size=18 align="center" color="#1974D2" weight="bold" underline=false italic=false} 
  labelFont={font size=14 family="'Open Sans', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif" color="#000000" align="center"}
| render

filters
| essql 
  query="SELECT 
SUM (passenger_count) as apis_total_passengers
FROM \"message-flight-idx\"
WHERE message_type = 'APIS'"
| math "apis_total_passengers"
| metric "Passengers - APIS" 
  metricFont={font family="'Open Sans', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif" size=18 align="center" color="#1974D2" weight="bold" underline=false italic=false} 
  labelFont={font size=14 family="'Open Sans', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif" color="#000000" align="center"}
| render
